This application is based on intent concept of android.
intent is basically primary component by which we can change one activity to another activity.
similarly this project is based on intent only ,here in the first activity i use two text field,and two buttons.
one text field accept user name and second text field will accept only number.
in the second activity i used one text field which will show user`s name and addition,multiplication and substraction of given number with 5
